OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwin turns into nightmare   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents in southern Mexico say they are
OL,6, being threatened by a gang after their 
OL,7, children's nursery won 20m pesos       
OL,8, ($950,000; #710,0000) in a lottery.    
OL,10,FThe nursery has just over two dozen    
OL,11,Fpupils and their parents were put in   
OL,12,Fcharge of administering the prize.     
OL,14,FSoon after their win was made public,  
OL,15,Fthey received threats from an armed    
OL,16,Fgroup, which demanded that they use the
OL,17,Fmoney to buy weapons for the gang.     
OL,19,FThe families say they had to flee their
OL,20,Fvillage and have been living rough.    
